%% Diagram: Message broadcast — sender to global subscribers
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CA as Client A (sender)
    participant WA as Webapp + Vitess
    participant AS as Admin Server
    participant CS as Channel Server (owner)
    participant GS as Gateway Servers (R1, R2)
    participant CB as Subscribers (R1, R2)

    CA->>WA: POST /chat.postMessage (via Envoy)
    WA->>WA: persist to Vitess
    WA->>AS: forward event (channel_id)
    AS->>AS: hash(channel_id) → owner CS
    AS->>CS: deliver event
    CS->>GS: broadcast to subscribed Gateways
    GS->>CB: WebSocket push to clients
    Note over CA,CB: Target end-to-end: <500 ms globally
